y want me as a treat and I only have 50 tricks left in my quiver. I'm off course by several clicks. I wanted to stay just outside the black hills so I could move easier and see my enemies before they saw me. However, I've been forced further and further off track by heavy resistance and now have to make 1 finally mad dash to the SW to make AB. This is my finally post from the field. Either I make it or I don't. If you hear from me here again then it will be to celebrate! If not...don't worry about the body. I'm sure it will decompose soon enough.<br>
Crow Darkstalker</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2f2f4f><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Crow</FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Unregistered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>10/30/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>9:59:49 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=304.topic&index=14><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I have looked into the face of Death ...</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">... and I spit right in his eye!! I MADE IT!!! hahahahah. Well, to finish the story...I was pinned down by 3 Extas Lugians. I waited for my debuffs to drop...re-buffed and then took a few shots at the lugies just for fun. needless to say i did not hit a single one of these 108 level giants. Turning SW I made my sprint to AB. I tried to follow the ridges as much as possible..but after Diamaond Golem number 3 showed up...I went down into the vallies and the swamps. When I came face to face with a Virindi and a few tusker slaves I knew I was gonna die. There were 2 bodies already littering the gorund...but somehow I dodged the worst of the spells...broke into the open and saw the buildings of AB on a small hilltop. Now...I'm gonna have a drink!!</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#6B8E23><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ugharadin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gharadin</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA